<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Marco J Poulter — Someone to talk to</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --sage: #6c63ff;
    --sage-light: #f0eeff;
    --sage-mid: #c4beff;
    --warm: #0a0a12;
    --text: #f0eeff;
    --text-muted: #b0a8e0;
    --text-light: #6e68a0;
    --border: rgba(108,99,255,0.2);
    --radius: 12px;
    --card-bg: #12101e;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--warm);
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(10,10,18,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .nav-name {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    color: #f0eeff;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; }
  .nav-links a {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--sage); }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 92vh;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 2rem 4rem;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    max-width: 680px;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--sage);
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 480px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
  .btn-primary {
    background: #6c63ff;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #5550d4; transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: #6c63ff; color: #6c63ff; }

  .scroll-hint {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .scroll-hint::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 1px; height: 40px;
    background: rgba(108,99,255,0.4);
  }

  /* SECTION SHARED */
  section { padding: 5rem 2rem; }
  .section-inner { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* ABOUT */
  #about { background: #12101e; }
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .about-text p { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .about-note {
    background: rgba(108,99,255,0.1);
    border-left: 3px solid #6c63ff;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius) var(--radius) 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* WHAT I OFFER */
  #offer { background: #0a0a12; }
  .offer-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }
  .offer-card {
    background: #1a1730;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  .offer-icon {
    width: 40px; height: 40px;
    background: rgba(108,99,255,0.15);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .offer-icon svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; stroke: var(--sage); fill: none; stroke-width: 1.5; }
  .offer-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .offer-card p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* NOT OFFER */
  .not-section {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    background: #1a1730;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
  }
  .not-section h3 {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .not-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .not-list li {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .not-list li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute; left: 0;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  /* HOW IT WORKS */
  #how { background: #12101e; }
  .steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; margin-top: 2.5rem; }
  .step { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; padding-bottom: 2.5rem; position: relative; }
  .step:not(:last-child)::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 19px; top: 40px; bottom: 0;
    width: 1px; background: rgba(108,99,255,0.3);
  }
  .step-num {
    width: 40px; height: 40px; flex-shrink: 0;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(108,99,255,0.4);
    background: rgba(108,99,255,0.15);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--sage);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .step-content h3 {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    padding-top: 0.6rem;
  }
  .step-content p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-muted); }

  /* CONNECT */
  #connect { background: var(--warm); }
  .connect-box {
    background: #1a1730;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }
  .connect-box p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; max-width: 440px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .discord-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(108,99,255,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(108,99,255,0.25);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', monospace;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--sage);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .connect-methods {
    display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  .connect-methods span { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .dot { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--sage-mid); display: inline-block; }

  /* T&C */
  #terms { background: #12101e; }
  .terms-box {
    background: rgba(108,99,255,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(108,99,255,0.25);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }
  .terms-box h3 {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .terms-box h3:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .terms-box p, .terms-box li { color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .terms-box ul { padding-left: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .terms-box li { margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .terms-date { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-light); margin-top: 1.5rem; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    background: var(--warm);
  }


    .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .faq-item summary {
    list-style: none;
  }
  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }
  .faq-q {
    width: 100%; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    padding: 1.1rem 0; font-size: 0.95rem; font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    color: var(--text); text-align: left; font-weight: 400;
  }
  .faq-q:hover { color: var(--sage); }
  .faq-arrow { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--sage); flex-shrink: 0; margin-left: 1rem; transition: transform 0.2s; }
  .faq-a { padding-bottom: 1rem; }
  .faq-a p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.8; }
  details[open] .faq-arrow { transform: rotate(45deg); }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    nav { padding: 1rem; }
    .nav-links { gap: 1rem; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
    section { padding: 3.5rem 1.25rem; }
    .connect-box { padding: 1.75rem 1.25rem; }
    .terms-box { padding: 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-name">Marco J Poulter</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#offer">What I offer</a>
    <a href="#how">How it works</a>
    <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
    <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="#terms">Terms</a>
    <a href="#connect">Contact</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <p class="hero-eyebrow">Online peer support &amp; listening</p>
  <h1>Sometimes you just need <em>someone to talk to</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">I'm Marco — a real person, not a therapist. I offer a calm, caring space to be heard, vent freely, and feel a little less alone. Available online, worldwide.</p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="#connect" class="btn-primary">Get in touch</a>
    <a href="#terms" class="btn-secondary">Read the terms first</a>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-hint">scroll</div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-label">About me</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">A genuine listener, available worldwide</h2>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>Hi, I'm Marco. I started this because I noticed how many people around me were struggling — not necessarily with something clinical, but just with the weight of everyday life. Stress, loneliness, confusion, heartbreak, feeling stuck. The kind of stuff that doesn't always need a therapist — it just needs someone who genuinely listens.</p>
        <p>I'm not a psychologist or counsellor and I won't pretend to be. What I bring is patience, real empathy, and zero judgement. I'll listen to whatever's on your mind, reflect it back honestly, and help you feel a little clearer by the end of our conversation.</p>
        <p>Think of it like talking to a friend who has the time and actually wants to hear you — because I do.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem;">
        <div style="border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; aspect-ratio: 3/4; max-height: 340px;">
          <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Marco J Poulter" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center top;" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-note">
          "I'm not here to fix you or diagnose anything. I'm here to listen, reflect, and make you feel a little less alone in whatever you're going through."
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OFFER -->
<section id="offer">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-label">What I offer</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Honest, human connection — nothing more</h2>

    <div class="offer-cards">
      <div class="offer-card">
        <div class="offer-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Active listening</h3>
        <p>I listen without interrupting, without judging, and without rushing you to a conclusion.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="offer-card">
        <div class="offer-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22c5.523 0 10-4.477 10-10S17.523 2 12 2 2 6.477 2 12s4.477 10 10 10z"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Thoughtful feedback</h3>
        <p>I'll share honest, caring reflections on what you share with me — a fresh, outside perspective.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="offer-card">
        <div class="offer-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>A caring presence</h3>
        <p>I genuinely care about the people I talk to. You won't feel like a transaction.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="offer-card">
        <div class="offer-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>A safe space</h3>
        <p>What you share stays between us. I won't repeat, screenshot, or share your conversations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="not-section">
      <h3>To be completely transparent — I am not, and do not offer:</h3>
      <ul class="not-list">
        <li>Therapy, counselling, or psychotherapy of any kind</li>
        <li>Clinical assessment, diagnosis, or treatment</li>
        <li>Crisis intervention or emergency mental health support</li>
        <li>Medical, psychiatric, or legal advice</li>
        <li>A substitute for a qualified mental health professional</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section id="how">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-label">How it works</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Simple, flexible, and on your terms</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Send me an email</h3>
          <p>Email me at <span style="user-select: all; color: #a09aff; font-weight: 500;">marcopoulter@gmail.com</span> with a brief intro — who you are, what's on your mind, and what you're looking for. There's no right or wrong way to write it. I'll read it personally and reply within 24 hours.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>We get acquainted</h3>
          <p>Once I've replied, we'll exchange a few messages over email to get comfortable. I'll share how we can connect for the actual session — whether that's Discord, Google Meet, or another platform that works for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>We agree on a time</h3>
          <p>We'll find a time that suits you. I work across time zones so just let me know where you are and we'll figure it out. Payment is confirmed before the session.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>We talk</h3>
          <p>You talk, I listen. No script, no structure — just a real conversation. I'll reflect back what I hear, ask gentle questions, and offer honest perspective if you'd like it. You set the pace.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">5</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>You leave feeling heard</h3>
          <p>That's the whole goal. If at any point it feels like you need more support than I can offer, I'll tell you honestly and point you toward the right resources — no hard feelings, ever.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section id="faq" style="background: #1a1730;">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-label">FAQ</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Common questions</h2>
    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Click any question below to read the answer. If something isn't covered here, just ask me in your first email.</p>
    <div style="margin-top: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0;">

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-q">What actually happens in a session? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span></summary>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>We hop on a call — Discord, Google Meet, or whatever works for you — and you talk. There's no structure or agenda. You lead, I follow. I'll listen carefully, reflect back what I hear, and ask gentle questions if it helps. If you want direct feedback or a fresh perspective, I'll give it. If you just want to vent without any input, that's completely fine too — just let me know.</p></div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-q">How long is a session? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span></summary>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Sessions are one hour at €15. If you feel like you need more or less time, just say so when you email me and we can figure out something that works.</p></div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-q">What if I just want to vent — no feedback? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span></summary>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Completely fine. Just mention it when we connect. Some people want to be heard without being responded to, and I'm totally comfortable with that. You set the tone.</p></div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-q">Is this confidential? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span></summary>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. I won't share, repeat, or screenshot anything you say. What you tell me stays between us. The only exception is if I have genuine reason to believe you're in serious danger — in that case I'll encourage you to contact emergency services, but I'm not a reporting authority.</p></div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-q">What if things get too heavy or serious? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span></summary>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>I'll always be honest with you. If it becomes clear that what you're dealing with needs more than I can offer — a real mental health professional, a crisis line, a doctor — I'll tell you directly and help point you in the right direction. I won't just keep taking your money if I'm not the right fit.</p></div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-q">Can I cancel or reschedule? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span></summary>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Yes — please give me at least 24 hours notice and I'll happily reschedule at no extra cost. Cancellations with less than 24 hours notice or no-shows are non-refundable, as that time was set aside for you. If something genuinely unexpected comes up, just message me and we'll work something out.</p></div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-q">This might be for me if... <span class="faq-arrow">+</span></summary>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>You're going through a breakup or relationship stress. You feel overwhelmed but don't know why. You need to think out loud. You're lonely and want a real conversation. You're stressed at work or in life and just need to offload. You're not in crisis, but you're not quite okay either. You want someone to talk to who genuinely listens — without booking a therapist.</p></div>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PRICING -->
<section id="pricing">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-label">Pricing</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Simple, honest pricing</h2>
    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">No hidden fees. No subscriptions. Just pay for the time we spend together.</p>
    <div style="background: #1a1730; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 2rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div>
        <div style="font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--sage);">€15 <span style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">/ hour</span></div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.875rem; margin-top: 0.4rem;">Payment details shared after your first email.</p>
        <p style="color: #a09aff; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; font-style: italic;">&#10024; First session may be free — I'm open to offering a trial so you can see if this is right for you. Just mention it in your email.</p>
